milestones.description: Niall O'Brien and Eoin Morgan's 80-run partnership is IRE's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 58 between Kyle McCallan and Andre Botha
Andre Botha and Eoin Morgan's 19-run partnership is IRE's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 3 between Gillespie and Andre Botha
Johnston and Eoin Morgan's 22-run partnership is IRE's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 8 between Andre Botha and Andrew White
Kyle McCallan and Eoin Morgan's 73-run partnership is IRE's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 1 between Andrew White and Dave Langford-Smith
Neil MacRae and Poonia's 20-run partnership is SCOT's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 19 between Ian Philip and Patterson
Ryan Watson and Poonia's 29-run partnership is SCOT's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 18 between Allingham and Ian Philip
John Blain and Craig Wright's 28-run partnership is SCOT's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 20 between John Blain and Alec Davies
Craig Wright and Paul Hoffmann's 23-run partnership is SCOT's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 20 between Hamilton and Asim Butt
Paul Hoffmann and Ross Lyons's 13-run partnership is SCOT's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 11 between Alec Davies and Nick Dyer
Eoin Morgan has become the top scorer for IRE in ODIs with 99 runs, going past Andre Botha's 52
Johnston has broken the record for most catches (3) in ODIs for IRE, going past Paul Mooney's 2
Niall O'Brien and Eoin Morgan's 80-run partnership is IRE's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 74 between Kevin O'Brien and Andrew White
Colin Smith has broken the record for most dismissals (4) in ODIs for SCOT, going past Alec Davies's 3
Colin Smith has broken the record for most dismissals in an innings (3) in ODIs for SCOT, going past Alec Davies's 2
Paul Hoffmann has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (4) in ODIs for SCOT, going past Hamilton's 3
Eoin Morgan's 99 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for IRE), surpassing Andre Botha's 52
Eoin Morgan has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (34) in an innings in ODIs for IRE, going past Andre Botha's 20
Gillespie has broken the record for most ducks (2) in ODIs for IRE, going past Dom Joyce's 1
Dave Langford-Smith has become the top wicket-taker for IRE in ODIs with 6 wickets, going past John Mooney's 3
Andre Botha has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (2) for IRE, going past Jeremy Bray
John Blain has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (7) for SCOT, going past Hamilton
